    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">BITBUCKET_USERNAME</code> should be your Bitbucket serverâ€™s username</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">BITBUCKET_PASSWORD</code> should be your Bitbucket serverâ€™s password</p>
  </li>
